These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, card-games, badmintoning
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, blue, chestnut, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship, bike, train
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, badminton, parkour, skiing
1. the person who likes blue is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person driving the bike is the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who's hobby is badmintoning is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
7. the person who likes blue is the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
9. the person who's hobby is badmintoning is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games  | badmintoning  | camping | card-games |
| Color           | blue | emerald | yellow  | chestnut  |
| Transport   | train       | bike      | snowmobile | ship      |
| Sport           | soccer          | badminton     | parkour    | skiing     |

