.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, backgammon, whist
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican, spanish, turkish
House: palace, art-deco, victorian, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, volleyball, water-polo
1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the mexican##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the palace house##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the victorian house##1
7. the art-deco house is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Game      | backgammon     | canasta       | mah-jongg | whist        |
| Nationality          | turkish     | mexican       | spanish   | pakistani   |
| House   | victorian      | art-deco       | gothic-revival     | palace    |
| Sport         | volleyball | water-polo | baseball | ice-hockey |

