.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, june, march
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, rock, r&b, country
There 4 different types of food: carrot, papaya, plum, kiwi
 1. the person drinking tea is the person eating kiwi##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 7. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Birthday           | may   | june | april   | march |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | rock    | country | r&b        |
| Food           | plum         | carrot  | kiwi       | papaya         |

