.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, firefighter, scientist
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, april, february
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, oliveros, dannemann, chaman
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping, drawing, reading
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
4. the scientist is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is on the right of the bartender##1
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | engineer   | bartender  | scientist | firefighter |
| Birthday   | april | february       | july       | december     |
| Cigar   | dannemann       | chaman    | oliveros     | aristoff  |
| Hobby           | camping     | drawing | reading     | rock-climbing         |

