.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, fuchsia, light-blue, turquise
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Color           | emerald  | light-blue    | fuchsia | turquise |
| Beverage   | soy-milk      | hot-chocolate    | lemonade         | coffee    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Pet         | frog | dog | chinchilla      | goldfish      |

