.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, country, indie
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, dancer, doctor, writer
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, light-blue, azure
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, baccarat, montecristo, blend
 1. the fan of country is the person who likes lavender##1
 2. the fan of salsa is the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the accountant is the person who likes lavender##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is the fan of salsa##1
 5. the person who likes light-blue is the writer##1
 6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the doctor is on the far left##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre          | salsa  | indie | country     | gospel |
| Job           | doctor  | writer      | accountant | dancer    |
| Color   | ebony | light-blue  | lavender    | azure  |
| Cigar           | montecristo   | blend       | bolivar       | baccarat      |

