4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, oliveros, prince, dannemann
There 4 different types of food: onion, broccoli, grapes, cranberry
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
 1. the person eating onion is the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the wooden house##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 4. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 6. the prince-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the person eating onion is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the left of the wooden house##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House    | townhouse | wooden     | cape-cod    | palace |
| Cigar       | montecristo | prince    | dannemann | oliveros |
| Food         | broccoli   | grapes  | cranberry        | onion    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

