6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
8. the owner of the horse is the person who likes azure##1
9. the owner of the ferret is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
