.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
City: san-francisco, colone, boston, edinburgh
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, traveling, video-games
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, monopoly, billiard
There 4 different types of food: potato, banana, pear, spinach
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person playing chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person eating banana##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| City      | san-francisco     | edinburgh           | colone    | boston    |
| Hobby         | traveling  | rock-climbing | drawing  | video-games |
| Game   | monopoly     | bridge     | chess | billiard   |
| Food         | spinach | potato     | banana | pear     |

