7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
9. the italian is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
